text: Vasile Huţanu (June 1, 1954 – February 24, 2014) was a Romanian ice hockey player. He played for the Romania men's national ice hockey team at the 1976 Winter Olympics in Innsbruck. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Competitors at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Romanian ice hockey players Category:Ice hockey centres
